Q_DESC: Given an array of strings, return a MapString, Boolean where each different string is a key and its value is true if that string appears 2 or more times in the array.
TESTCASE_1:
a a b b c
###---###SEPERATOR---###---
a true
b true
c false
TESTCASE_2:
yes no yes no yes
###---###SEPERATOR---###---
no true
yes true
TESTCASE_3:
cat bat cat bat axe
###---###SEPERATOR---###---
axe false
bat true
cat true
TESTCASE_4:
universe is not safe
###---###SEPERATOR---###---
is false
not false
safe false
universe false
